This market will immediately resolve to "Yes" if any Binance 1 minute candle for Solana (SOLUSDT) between November 1, 2024, 00:00 and November 30, 2024, 23:59 in the ET timezone has a final "High" price of $200.00 or higher. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No."
